00:39.999 --> 00:42.365
Okay. Fine.
I'm a freak,
all right?

00:42.460 --> 00:44.166
Claire. Shut up.

00:46.964 --> 00:48.295
CLAIRE: What's on
yourneck?

00:48.382 --> 00:51.089
Last thing I remember
is this man stepping
out of the bushes,

00:51.177 --> 00:52.166
calling my name.

00:52.261 --> 00:53.501
What are you
talking about?
What man?

00:53.596 --> 00:55.678
The guy with
the horn-rimmed
glasses.

00:55.765 --> 00:57.847
MOHINDER ON PHONE:
I’m sending you a JPEG
ofa painting / found.

