looking at him, but
this dog can power walk.

01:21.499 --> 01:23.785
Have you talked
to Claire lately?

01:23.876 --> 01:25.036
About what?

01:25.127 --> 01:28.164
Oh, just about
how she's adjusting.

01:28.256 --> 01:30.793
Has she met somebody?
A boy, maybe?

01:31.676 --> 01:34.088
If the wrong person
comes into her life,
it could be...

01:35.429 --> 01:37.385
problematic
for all of us.

01:37.473 --> 01:39.009
What makes you
so sure it's a boy?

01:39.100 --> 01:41.682
What makes you
so sure it isn't?

01:49.193 --> 01:50.603
Is there
something
on my face?

01:50.695 --> 01:52.981
Claire, your mother and I
need to talk to you.

01:53.698 --> 01:54.938
About boys.

01:55.032 --> 01:56.408
Please,
not the sex
talk again.

01:56.492 --> 01:58.323
It was painful enough
the first time.

01:58.411 --> 02:00.242
We just want to
know if you're
seeing anyone.

02:00.329 --> 02:01.785
