is forbidden too?

02:01.872 --> 02:03.453
Along with cheerleading
and a social life.

02:03.541 --> 02:05.077
Nobody's forbidding
anything, Claire.

02:05.167 --> 02:09.285
It's just that
any outsider could be
a threat to the family.

02:09.880 --> 02:13.122
Dad, believe it or not,
there are people in this world
who aren't out to get us.

02:13.217 --> 02:17.051
Al| we're saying is,
if there is a boy,
I'd like to meet him.

02:17.305 --> 02:21.014
We could help you decide
whether this is somebody
that you could trust.

02:27.398 --> 02:28.433
(SCOFFS)

02:28.524 --> 02:29.889
Dad, relax.

02:31.027 --> 02:33.143
