02:43.748 --> 02:45.238
(SCREAMING)

02:47.376 --> 02:48.331
(WHISPERING)
Okay. It's okay.

02:48.419 --> 02:49.499
(CRYING) I'm sorry.
I can't help it.

02:51.797 --> 02:53.708
(SHUSHING)
It's okay.
Get the light.

02:56.177 --> 02:57.508
MOHINDER: Molly?
MATT: She's fine.

02:57.595 --> 02:59.335
Okay, put your head down.

03:00.056 --> 03:01.842
It's over. Right?

03:01.932 --> 03:04.719
Okay. You want
something to drink?

03:04.810 --> 03:06.766
Water.
Water. Okay.

03:09.023 --> 03:10.388
(SIGHING)

03:13.944 --> 03:15.650
