03:15.946 --> 03:18.858
Two a night now.
I'm trying to listen in,
get in her head.

03:18.949 --> 03:20.200
And I keep
getting
thrown back.

03:20.284 --> 03:21.524
So what are we
supposed to do?

03:21.619 --> 03:22.654
I don't know.
You're the scientist.

03:22.745 --> 03:24.861
That doesn't exactly
make me an expert
on nightmares.

03:24.955 --> 03:27.082
Well,
that makes
two of us.

03:28.334 --> 03:32.703
(SIGHING) I don't know. I'll
go get the water. Just keep
her calm and we'll just...

03:32.797 --> 03:34.662
Figure it out. Right?

03:42.348 --> 03:44.714
(WHISPERING) Just try
to get some sleep,
sweetheart.

03:44.809 --> 03:46.765
