Listen, I wanted to tell you
that your grandmother's
in the hospital.

04:26.350 --> 04:27.430
Is she okay?

04:27.518 --> 04:29.429
Yeah.
She's gonna
be fine.

04:29.520 --> 04:31.761
But when you get home,
I want you to get your mommy

04:31.856 --> 04:33.016
