04:33.107 --> 04:34.643
'Cause I know
she's gonna wanna
hear from you.

04:34.733 --> 04:36.985
Okay.

04:37.862 --> 04:41.525
I know I haven't
been around and
I'm sorry about that.

04:45.202 --> 04:48.285
But I'm
coming home.
I promise.

04:49.957 --> 04:52.039
And what do Petrellis do
when they make promises?

04:52.126 --> 04:53.115
Keep them!
Keep them.

04:53.210 --> 04:54.325
That's right.

04:54.420 --> 04:56.126
Can I help you?

04:56.213 --> 04:57.202
I'm their father.

04:57.423 --> 05:00.210
You know
you're not allowed
to be here.

05:02.803 --> 05:03.792
Go ahead.

05:03.888 --> 05:05.469
No. Iwant to
stay with you.

05:05.556 --> 05:07.171
It's okay.

05:07.266 --> 05:08.506
Go on.

05:10.060 --> 05:12.346
See you soon. Okay?

05:12.438 --> 05:13.769
Go ahead.

05:30.080 --> 05:32.036
So you are from California?

05:32.124 --> 05:33.455
California?

05:33.876 --> 05:34.911
MAYA: Uh-huh.

05:35.002 --> 05:38.460
The license on the car.
It says California.

05:38.547 --> 05:41.960
Oh. That. No,
I just picked
the car up there.

05:42.051 --> 05:44.087
I'm actually
from Jersey.

05:44.178 --> 05:46.669
This is very,
very close
to New York.

05:46.847 --> 05:48.223
We are going to New York.
My brother and me...

05:53.020 --> 05:55.136
chances are
they're gonna be
looking for all of us.

05:55.231 --> 05:56.937
(BOTH SPEAKING SPANISH)

05:58.108 --> 05:59.894
(BRAKES SCREECHING)

06:19.296 --> 06:21.036
(SPEAKING SPANISH)

06:21.131 --> 06:22.792
DEREK: Dude looks dead.

06:27.388 --> 06:28.673
(GASPING) Help me.

06:50.494 --> 06:52.155
DAMON: Micah.

06:53.330 --> 06:54.866
Micah.

06:57.251 --> 06:58.912
Wake up, fool!

07:04.967 --> 07:07.083
Morning, boys.
You ready for school?

07:07.177 --> 07:08.132
MICAH: Yes, ma'am.

07:08.220 --> 07:09.426
(IMITATING MICAH)
Yes, ma'am.

07:09.513 --> 07:13.722
You watch your tongue,
young man.
He's a guest in our house.

07:13.809 --> 07:15.720
