07:15.811 --> 07:17.767
Nana, I need $65.

07:17.855 --> 07:20.221
That's funny. So do I.

07:20.316 --> 07:21.931
MONICA:
Good morning,
everybody.

07:22.026 --> 07:24.938
Well, do I look
any different today?

07:25.029 --> 07:26.815
Just as lame
as you always do.

07:26.905 --> 07:28.520
You look confident.

07:28.616 --> 07:29.901
MONICA:
"Confident" is good.

07:29.992 --> 07:32.699
How about
"in charge"?
Micah?

07:32.786 --> 07:35.038
Yeah. You look like
someone who's in charge.

07:35.122 --> 07:37.283
And why do I look like
someone who's in charge?

07:37.374 --> 07:39.365
Because somebody died
and left you that way?

07:39.460 --> 07:43.453
No. Because today
is the day they're posting
the test results

07:43.547 --> 07:45.458
for the regional manager
training program.

07:45.549 --> 07:48.006
The test I just
happened to
have aced.

07:48.093 --> 07:49.173
All right.

07:49.261 --> 07:52.094
Good, so now you can afford
that $65 I asked you for.

07:52.181 --> 07:53.387
MONICA: No, I can't.

07:53.515 --> 07:57.133
And don't be asking
Grandma, either. Don't
give him a dime, Nana.

07:57.227 --> 07:59.969
