08:12.993 --> 08:16.906
You should be watching
something educational.
Like this.

08:16.997 --> 08:18.828
This is good TV.

08:19.792 --> 08:22.158
WOMAN ON TV: And voila.
You have a beautiful
tomato rose.

08:22.252 --> 08:24.664
Making flowers
out of tomatoes?

08:25.255 --> 08:26.995
(CHUCKLES) Who's got
time to do that?

08:27.091 --> 08:29.082
