08:31.303 --> 08:34.215
(SIGHING) I'll bring
dinner home
from the restaurant.

08:35.224 --> 08:37.886
Again. Wish me luck.

08:39.269 --> 08:40.258
Break a leg.

08:40.354 --> 08:41.434
Whatever.

08:45.526 --> 08:47.232
(DOOR CLOSING)

08:47.319 --> 08:48.900
What are you looking at?

08:48.987 --> 08:50.022
Nothing.

08:51.073 --> 08:52.609
It's just...

08:52.700 --> 08:55.533
I think I know a way
to get you Pay-Per-View.

08:59.707 --> 09:03.165
I did it.
I killed
Kaito Nakamura.

09:04.169 --> 09:05.420
VVhy?

09:06.296 --> 09:07.877
ForaH
the reasons
you said.

09:07.965 --> 09:09.671
Sex? Money?

09:09.758 --> 09:10.918
Yes.

09:11.468 --> 09:13.424
You know I was on the roof.

09:13.512 --> 09:17.471
You have my fingerprints.
I did it. I pushed him off.

09:19.768 --> 09:23.010
When we brought you in,
you tried to kill yourself.

09:23.981 --> 09:25.562
Turns out your wounds
were self-inflicted.

09:25.649 --> 09:27.059
l was distraught.

09:27.151 --> 09:31.895
Overwhelmed by what I did
and so I... l attacked myself.

09:34.491 --> 09:37.233
ANGELA: Write down
the statement and
let it go, Parkman.

09:37.327 --> 09:39.488
Please. Let it go.

09:39.913 --> 09:41.494
(CLEARS THROAT)

09:43.167 --> 09:46.580
Mrs. Petrelli,
why are you
doing this?

09:46.670 --> 09:49.503
My head is clear now.
I understand.

09:50.257 --> 09:53.249
The only way out of this
is for me to confess.

09:54.178 --> 09:57.341
Fine. Let's start
the paperwork.

10:00.142 --> 10:04.385
ANGELA: If they keep digging
they will find out about all
of us and what we can do.

10:05.355 --> 10:06.856
Let it go.

10:08.066 --> 10:09.442
Let it go.

10:16.950 --> 10:17.985
What's that?

10:18.076 --> 10:20.533
Parental release form
to try out for
the cheerleading squad.

10:20.621 --> 10:22.486
For me?
Yup.

10:23.624 --> 10:26.957
l'm flattered. I don't think
I can squeeze cheerleading
into my schedule.

10:27.044 --> 10:29.535
But you're kind of a hero
to the girls in the squad.

10:29.630 --> 10:30.915
A hero? Why?

10:31.006 --> 10:32.917
The way
you stood up to Debbie
on your first day.

10:33.008 --> 10:35.465
You know, half of
being a cheerleader
is having guts.

10:35.552 --> 10:37.929
And you have got
those in spades.

10:40.891 --> 10:42.802
I'll tell you what.
I'll think about it

10:42.893 --> 10:45.259
and then I'll let you know
if I change my mind.

10:45.354 --> 10:48.767
Good, then take
the release form
just in case.

10:51.026 --> 10:52.937
Hi.

10:53.028 --> 10:54.063
Hi.

10:54.738 --> 10:57.480
I can't stop thinking
about yesterday.
It was so amazing.

10:57.574 --> 11:00.316
I finally have someone
I can be myselfwith.

11:00.410 --> 11:02.492
(SCHOOL BELL RINGING)

11:02.579 --> 11:04.194
About that...

11:04.289 --> 11:07.076
I'm not sure
we should
hang out anymore.

11:09.419 --> 11:12.502
It's just my parents
are really overprotective.

11:12.589 --> 11:14.875
Is this because
we flew together?

11:15.008 --> 11:16.999
I weirded you out,
didn't I?
No.

11:17.094 --> 11:18.334
I like you.
I really do.

11:18.428 --> 11:22.216
Then it's those marks on
my neck, right? You think
I was abducted by aliens.

11:22.307 --> 11:23.843
I told you, it was a guy
with horn-rimmed glasses.

11:23.934 --> 11:25.424
It's my dad.

11:27.354 --> 11:30.938
He's just really
overprotective
about the dating thing.

11:32.025 --> 11:33.526
Then let me talk to him.

11:33.610 --> 11:35.987
I don't think
that's a good idea.

11:36.071 --> 11:37.277
(EXHALES) But...

11:38.740 --> 11:41.072
I can fly,
and you
can regenerate.

11:41.159 --> 11:43.115
I mean, doesn't that
tell you anything?

11:43.203 --> 11:46.411
Please don't make this
harder on me than it
already is.

11:49.126 --> 11:51.492
Okay, I'll tell you what.

11:51.712 --> 11:54.078
Tomorrow I'll
totally back off.

11:54.172 --> 11:55.878
Today, I'm asking you out.

11:55.966 --> 11:56.955
West, I...

11:57.050 --> 11:58.790
Tonight.
Anywhere you
want to go.

11:58.886 --> 12:01.798
If you want to
call it off
after that, fine.

12:05.851 --> 12:07.887
Fine. Butjust this once.

12:09.146 --> 12:10.807
You won't regret it.

12:17.654 --> 12:20.031
What do you think
you're doing questioning
a suspect in a hospital?

12:20.115 --> 12:22.276
Any confession
is coerced.
She's sick.

12:22.367 --> 12:24.653
Coerced or not,
they believe her.

12:26.955 --> 12:29.037
But I know she's innocent.

12:30.208 --> 12:31.368
How?

12:38.759 --> 12:40.124
(SIGHING)

12:42.429 --> 12:45.091
(WHISPERING)
The same way I know
that you can fly.

12:46.850 --> 12:49.808
I can read your mind.
Just like I read
your mother's.

12:49.895 --> 12:53.103
But I can't tell my partner
what I know or how I know it.

12:53.190 --> 12:55.647
Are you reading
my mind right now?

12:55.734 --> 12:56.769
No.

12:56.860 --> 12:58.396
Yes. I'm sorry.

13:01.531 --> 13:03.487
Look, your mother
thinks she's protecting
somebody

13:03.575 --> 13:04.690
by shutting down
this investigation.

13:04.785 --> 13:06.446
But I'm not gonna
let it happen.
I'm not backing down.

13:06.536 --> 13:08.663
I got a little girl at home
who wakes up in
the middle of the night

13:08.747 --> 13:12.956
screaming about nightmares
and drawing a symbol that...

13:13.627 --> 13:17.040
This. The same symbol
that's on these photos.

13:18.632 --> 13:19.963
I know this symbol.

13:20.050 --> 13:22.462
(WHISPERING) I think
it's all connected.
Everything.

13:22.552 --> 13:25.419
What you and I can do?
We're all connected.

13:26.556 --> 13:28.092
I know this photograph.

13:28.183 --> 13:30.640
Good. Because
I need your help.

13:30.727 --> 13:34.185
I can't continue
this investigation
without you.

13:35.899 --> 13:37.560
All right. I'II...

13:39.236 --> 13:41.477
I need five minutes
alone with my mother.

13:41.697 --> 13:42.903
Alone.

13:53.166 --> 13:56.499
Why are you confessing
to a crime
you didn't commit?

13:58.463 --> 14:00.419
Because
you were right,
Nathan.

14:00.507 --> 14:02.168
I don't deserve to be saved.

14:02.259 --> 14:05.171
Mom, I was angry when
I said that. l was drunk.
I didn't mean it.

14:05.262 --> 14:07.002
Of course you did.

14:08.473 --> 14:11.590
You asked me for help once.
Nowjust let me help you.

14:12.310 --> 14:16.019
Just because you've shaved
doesn't mean you're clean
and sober.

14:16.106 --> 14:18.973
You still have
to get yourself
into a program.

14:19.067 --> 14:22.901
Get your family back.
Don't let your children
hate you.

14:23.071 --> 14:25.357
Not if you can help it.

14:27.117 --> 14:29.779
You didn't kill
Kaito Nakamura.
I know that.

14:29.870 --> 14:32.452
I have done so many
bad things in my life.

14:32.539 --> 14:34.951
It really doesn't matter
what crime I confess to.

14:35.042 --> 14:36.031
Let me help you, Mom.

14:36.126 --> 14:37.491
No. What you want
is redemption.

14:37.586 --> 14:41.170
And you're not gonna
get it by helping me.
You'll just get killed.

14:41.256 --> 14:43.918
And I can't bear
to lose another son.

14:56.021 --> 14:58.262
(CLEARS THROAT)
He has to do this.
I'm sorry.

14:58.356 --> 15:00.483
That's all right.
I'm ready.

15:27.844 --> 15:30.335
Where's your stuff?
You're traveling
pretty light.

15:30.430 --> 15:32.011
I got robbed.

15:32.682 --> 15:35.594
Been walking for three days.
Thank God you came along.

15:35.685 --> 15:37.346
(SPEAKING SPANISH)

15:38.480 --> 15:40.266
Where are you going?

15:40.607 --> 15:43.770
I'm going home.
To America.
New York.

15:43.860 --> 15:44.849
New York.

15:45.237 --> 15:47.353
This is where
we're going.

15:47.906 --> 15:49.612
Do you have family there?

15:49.699 --> 15:50.825
No.

15:53.036 --> 15:54.276
We need to find this man.

15:54.371 --> 15:55.406
Maya, no.

15:55.497 --> 15:56.953
Dr. Suresh.

16:00.669 --> 16:03.786
Well this is a coincidence.
I know this book.
I've read it.

16:03.880 --> 16:04.960
Really?

16:09.719 --> 16:12.461
Why are you
searching for
Dr. Suresh?

16:12.556 --> 16:14.968
For, how you say this...

16:15.058 --> 16:16.889
Answers.
To what?

16:20.147 --> 16:22.012
I know Dr. Suresh.

16:23.692 --> 16:25.182
We're old friends.

16:25.277 --> 16:26.483
You and Dr. Suresh?

16:26.570 --> 16:30.813
You've helped me, now
I can return the favor.
I can take you to him.

16:30.907 --> 16:32.898
I can help you find him.

16:32.993 --> 16:34.779
(BOTH SPEAKING SPANISH)

16:49.426 --> 16:51.917
Thank you.
I don't know
what to say.

16:52.012 --> 16:53.923
I don't even
know your name.

16:54.014 --> 16:55.174
It's Gabriel.

16:58.560 --> 17:00.642
Gabriel Gray.

17:00.729 --> 17:01.764
Gabriel.

17:01.855 --> 17:02.844
(GASPING)

17:02.939 --> 17:04.600
Like the angel.

17:05.984 --> 17:07.099
Yeah.

17:09.070 --> 17:10.856
Just like the angel.

17:14.659 --> 17:17.116
(SINGING)
/ spent oh so many nights
just feeling sorry for myself

17:18.288 --> 17:21.530
/ used to cry
But now / hold
