17:21.625 --> 17:24.583
They've got rules against
drinking on the job, you know.

17:24.794 --> 17:26.750
It's all about
attitude, Camille.

17:26.838 --> 17:28.749
(SCOFFS)
What's about
aﬂﬂude?

